  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency enzyme-adapter-preact-pure to v2.1.0",
  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| [enzyme-adapter-preact-pure](https://togithub.com/preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure) | devDependencies | minor | [`2.0.2` -> `2.1.0`](https://renovatebot.com/diffs/npm/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure/2.0.2/2.1.0) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure</summary>\n\n### [`v2.1.0`](https://togithub.com/preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;210---2019-10-03)\n\n[Compare Source](https://togithub.com/preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure/compare/v2.0.2...v2.1.0)\n\n-   Fix `simulateError` under Preact 10.0.0 [#&#8203;75](https://togithub.com/preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure/pull/75)\n-   Make Preact v10 the default version internally. Preact v8 support will eventually\n    be removed in a future major release. [#&#8203;76](https://togithub.com/preactjs/enzyme-adapter-preact-pure/pull/76)\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\n - [ ] <!-- renovate-rebase -->If you want to rebase/retry this PR, check this box\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://togithub.com/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
